es found.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe verifier is implemented as a standalone utility. Future tasks should integrate this into the main PAL workflow or `verify_pal_workflow_artifacts` to ensure automatic secret checking of all runs.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-020@20260515t214233z-verify.md"}}
